description: Daniel Verlaan joined the meeting after the Dutch defence minister posted login details on Twitter.
title: Dutch journalist gatecrashes EU defence video conference
title_page: Dutch journalist gatecrashes EU defence video conference - BBC News
maintext: "After a number of attempts, RTL Nieuws succeeded in guessing the PIN code of the secret consultation, because five of the six digits of the pin code were visible in the photo," the news outlet said.
